---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Moveroo | Transport Terms & Conditions"
	description="Understand the terms governing vehicle and freight transport services with Moveroo, including responsibilities, charges, and liability."
	canonical="https://moveroo.com.au/terms-and-conditions-transport/"
>
	<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-slate-50 to-slate-100 py-24 dark:from-slate-900 dark:via-slate-800 dark:to-slate-900">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400">Transport Terms</p>
			<h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Understanding our transport agreement</h1>
			<p class="mt-6 text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
				These terms outline how Moveroo delivers vehicle and freight transport services across Australia. Review them carefully—they clarify responsibilities, charges, liability and how we manage bookings.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-white py-20 dark:bg-slate-900">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-12 px-6 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Key definitions</h2>
				<ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
					<li><strong>Charge Rate</strong>: $55 (ex GST) per 15 minutes for a two-person crew, unless otherwise quoted.</li>
					<li><strong>Goods</strong>: Items you ask us to transport.</li>
					<li><strong>Quote</strong>: The written estimate we supply.</li>
					<li><strong>Services</strong>: Any transport or ancillary work we perform for you.</li>
					<li><strong>Subcontractor</strong>: Partners appointed by Moveroo to assist with your move.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Application of these terms</h2>
				<p>
					These terms apply whenever you engage Moveroo, once you have had reasonable opportunity to review them. Proceeding with a booking confirms your acceptance.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Not common carriers</h2>
				<p>
					Moveroo is not a common carrier and may refuse to transport particular items or classes of goods at its discretion.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Your obligations & warranties</h2>
				<ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
					<li>Provide accurate information when requesting a quote or booking.</li>
					<li>Confirm you own the goods or are authorised to act on behalf of the owner.</li>
					<li>Disclose dangerous, fragile or high-value goods; we may refuse items that pose risks.</li>
					<li>Ensure all goods intended for transport are ready and you (or a representative) are present at loading and unloading.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Method of carriage</h2>
				<p>
					We may choose the route, vehicle type and subcontractors used. Any liability limits within these terms extend to our subcontractors and personnel.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Delivery</h2>
				<ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
					<li>Goods are delivered only to you or someone you nominate in writing.</li>
					<li>If delivery cannot proceed, storage fees and re-delivery charges may apply.</li>
					<li>We are not liable for delays caused by factors beyond our control.</li>
					<li>A week’s notice is required to retrieve goods from storage.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Charges & rescheduling</h2>
				<ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
					<li>Fees follow the accepted Quote. Changes to the scope or inaccurate information may incur adjustments.</li>
					<li>Storage is charged weekly and payable monthly in advance.</li>
					<li>Delays beyond 30 minutes outside our control may attract additional charges.</li>
					<li>Cancellation is fully refundable within 2 days of paying the deposit. After that, deposits are non-refundable but transferable within 12 months.</li>
					<li>Rescheduling within 7 days of the move date incurs a 50% administrative fee of the deposit.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Additional costs & lien</h2>
				<ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
					<li>You must reimburse any customs, quarantine or similar charges.</li>
					<li>We retain a lien over goods until all amounts owed are paid. After 28 days of non-payment, we may sell goods following notice.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Loss, damage & insurance</h2>
				<p>
					Guarantees under Australian Consumer Law may apply unless the services are for business purposes. We are not responsible for losses from events outside our control or inadequate packaging. You are responsible for arranging insurance cover for your goods.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Privacy & general terms</h2>
				<p>
					Personal information is handled per our <a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>. These terms are governed by Queensland law, with disputes referred to mediation under Queensland Law Society guidance.
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
